{"tid":2422672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國麻辣鍋可能致死！美國急全面召回 包裝曝光","createTime":"2021-02-25T10:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T11:21:21.000Z","uid":32511,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3c70575d503d5c807ef2e88bfde424c90081db1c","tid":2422672,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"美國食品安全檢查局（FSIS）下令，召回中國進口的麻辣火鍋料，理由是從不符合牛肉生產的條件的國家進口，其中含有牛脂成分，又沒有經過FSIS複檢，呼籲民眾全面回收，否則吃了可能會致死。<br />\n <br />\n恐造成健康危害 美急召回中國麻辣鍋<br />\n美國農業部在官網公布，目前正在召回一批大約96,810磅的牛肉牛脂產品，這些產品是從中國進口，但中國不是符合牛肉生產條件的國家，進口的這些產品沒有經過FSIS複檢，吃下去可能造成健康危害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/E21dGa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FE21dGa&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=2aff5c34\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/E21dGa</a>"},{"pid":"72b0b004fb03f59df995558ae1458c40599420cd","tid":2422672,"uid":224533,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"支那殺敵從來不廢一槍一炮，一兵一卒"},{"pid":"5524043b5f161a51833fe73ecbb3365fa5020f4d","tid":2422672,"uid":258696,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:55:29.000Z","msg":"支那国終於諗到稱霸世界既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50661420fef90d62ec83159270bc351e88a10ac","tid":2422672,"uid":321002,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"美國人應該唔會食，剩係華人先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80d9b0e56614167f1a568871ac6e54c0d6bb7f5","tid":2422672,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"國民黨會唔會走出嚟話美國食品都唔係好安全啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g